<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[الرَّاضية]</span>: قوله تعالى: عِيشَةٍ رااضِيَةٍ* <span class="c2">«٢»</span>.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
